BULL DURHAM - 1988

IMDb Rating: 7.0

   Crash Davis (Kevin Costner) is a savvy veteran catcher who dispenses his wisdom on a young fireballer Nuke Laloosh (Tim Robbins). Crash knows his career is winding down and he'll never fully realize his baseball dreams, but he can give back to the game he loves by helping the ignorant Nuke. Between the two of them is Annie (Susan Sarandon). Every season she picks a player who she dates for the season and dispenses her own brand of wisdom.
